Burning problems resolved:

Just downed this a couple of days ago. Plays fine on my pc (PowerDVD), but wouldn't do so on my stand-alone recorder (Sony). Solution:

Extract the rars (no errors found) then extract the IMG-file. Either burn it on a rewriteable or use the emulator ("fake burner") that comes with Nero. Then just burn de Video and Audio folders you have using Nero's DVD-Video mode.
